Sep 19, 2022
This is simple Highest high and Lowest low strategy.
Buy when break HH+offset
Sell when break LL+offset
Offset = (HH-LL)/2
Sep 17, 2024
Release Notes
The next stage of development of this strategy. The results of tests showed that it is much better to use Bollinger bands as a defining channel. Which was done in this modification.
